(321, 'ITCS-4001', 'candice.fung', '0000-00-00', 'Hong Kong', 'Product Manager (IP Services)', 'We are looking for Product Managers supporting the IP Services product management for a regional telecommunications in HK. The main responsibility is to manage the promising data product, having to oversee the product development and life-cycle.', '<ul><li>Understand the overall market and competitive space &ndash; and determine market segmentation, product pricing, positioning, and more</li><li>Convey that strategy in the form of a short- and long-term product roadmap, prioritizing features based on level of importance and time to execute</li><li>Conduct market researches, prepare analysis reports and recommendations.&nbsp;</li><li>Preparing proposal and request with potential business</li><li>Help coordinate and support the different teams that go into product creation &mdash; business, engineering, design, sales, marketing, and support teams</li></ul>', '<ul><li>University graduate preferably from Business Administration,&nbsp;Engineering or related disciplines</li><li>Minimum&nbsp;5 years&nbsp;relevant experience&nbsp;from ICT and telecom&nbsp;for enterprise</li><li>Candidate&nbsp;with IP product development experience</li><li>Presentable, self-motivated and social</li><li>Good written and spoken English and Chinese and Mandarin</li></ul>', '2016-11-01', 'inactive', '2016-11-01', 'LaaLaa  Tang', 'jobdetails.php?ID=&#34ITCS-1367&#34'),
(322, 'ITCS-3112', 'candice.fung', '0000-00-00', 'Hong Kong', 'Helpdesk Engineer', 'Our client is an international leading company in the industry who provides world class professional service. Currently, they are looking for talent in their technology department to join them and grow their exciting career here. Candidates can develop their strength and transfer to specific teams with satisfactory performance. ', '<ul><li>Provide first line support for internal staff with mostly application and hardware support</li><li>Conduct functional support on request</li><li>Take part in project to maximize exposure for future job rotation</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Higher Diploma in Computer Science/ Engineering or related disciplines</li><li>Solid IT support exposure</li><li>Self-motivated, team player with good communications skills</li><li>Good command of English, Cantonese and Mandarin</li></ul>', '2016-11-01', 'inactive', '2016-11-01', 'LaaLaa  Tang', 'jobdetails.php?ID=&#34ITCS-3112&#34'),
(323, 'ITCS-3234', 'candice.fung', '0000-00-00', 'Hong Kong', 'Senior Pricing Analyst', 'We are looking for Senior Pricing Analyst supporting the vigorous expanding activities from this market leading company in HK. The main responsibility is to manage the pricing analysis and maintain competitive price. He/ She would be supported by resourceful and great team and management.', '<ul><li>Conduct pricing analysis and ensure the price competitivenessfor the data telecommunications product</li><li>Maintain good relationship with vendor as well as carrier in the region</li><li>Collaborate with sales and marketing department and assist in order management</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Degree holder in Statistics, Business Administration, Finance or relevant disciplines</li><li>Minimum 3 years of experience in pricing in Telecommunication industry</li><li>Analytical, organised and self-motivated</li><li>Good communication skills with verbal and written Chinese and English</li></ul>', '2016-11-01', 'inactive', '2016-11-01', 'LaaLaa  Tang', 'jobdetails.php?ID=&#34ITCS-3234&#34'),
(324, 'ITCS-4002', 'candice.fung', '0000-00-00', 'Hong Kong', 'Senior Business Analyst/ Project Analyst (Retail)', 'Our client, a reputable retail group, is seeking a Senior Business Analyst/ Project Analyst to join their dynamic team to support their local and regional projects on store space management.', '<ul><li>Collaborate closely with IT Team and business stakeholders to collect and document business requirements</li><li>Support projects on store space planning and ensure quality deliverables</li><li>Manage change requests submission, screening and development progress</li><li>Analyze business workflow and provide suggestions on workflow improvement</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Degree holder in Information Systems, Industrial Engineering or relevant discipline</li><li>Min. 3 years solid experience as Business Analyst or Project Analyst in business process re-engineering projects</li><li>Experience in Retail/ Space Planning and knowledge in AutoCAD is an advantage</li><li>Good communication skills in verbal and written English and Chinese</li></ul>', '2016-11-01', 'inactive', '2016-11-01', 'LaaLaa  Tang', 'jobdetails.php?ID=&#34ITCS-4002&#34'),
(325, 'ITCS-1380', 'candice.fung', '0000-00-00', 'Hong Kong', 'Business Solutions Manager (Global top-tier professional IT solutions)', 'We are looking for Solution Consultant supporting the pre-sales role for a world leading vendor in HK. The main responsibility is to manage the promising product of business intelligence/ statistics software', '<ul><li>Manage and provide professional advise on the communications solution for the clients</li><li>Advise on the tender and other negotiation e.g. contract with support from diverse team for operation</li><li>Take parts in some pitching platform e.g. events like seminars, conference</li><li>Coordinate with different departments to ensure smooth operation</li></ul>', '<ul><li>University graduate preferably from Satistics,&nbsp;Engineering, Computer Engineering or related disciplines</li><li>Minimum 8 years&nbsp;relevant technical presales experience</li><li>Candidate with vendor exposure is preferred</li><li>Candidate with statistics software exposure will be of top priority</li><li>Presentable, self-motivated and sociable</li><li>Good written and spoken English and Chinese and Mandarin</li></ul>', '2016-11-01', 'inactive', '2016-11-01', 'LaaLaa  Tang', 'jobdetails.php?ID=&#34ITCS-1380&#34'),
