(1, 1, '<style>\nh6 {\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\n}\n</style>IT Consulting and Project Management', 'images/service1.jpg', 'The ITCS Group specialises in enabling organisations to deliver change within their IT environment. Our clients approach ITCS to deliver projects typically brought about by significant events such as mergers, acquisitions, in/out sourcing initiatives or major capital investments.\r\n \r\n</br> </br> <strong> Mergers & Acquisitions </strong>\r\n\r\n</br> </br> Mergers & Acquisitions present challenges to IT organisations that are not seen during Business As Usual activity. The scale of both technology and organisational transformation requires specific experience, knowledge and cultural sensitivity to ensure a successful outcome.\r\n</br> </br> Our experience includes IT business and technology management and our services include:\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Resource planning </li>\r\n<li> In/outsourcing management </li>\r\n<li> Contract renegotiation or novation </li>\r\n<li> IT to business alignment </li>\r\n<li> IT strategy </li>\r\n<li> Change and migration planning </li>\r\n<li> Program and Project management </li>\r\n<li> IT Infrastructure integration services </li>\r\n<li> Application migration </li>\r\n<li> Integration and consolidation </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n \r\n</br> <strong> Corporate Real Estate investment </strong>\r\n</br> </br> ITCS Group understands the importance of correctly specifying and delivering IT infrastructure in relation to real estate projects. We are engaged throughout the project life cycle to work along side Corporate Real Estate, Facilities Management, Construction Project Management, Quantity Surveyors, Interior Designers and Mechanical & Electrical Engineering to ensure that the business&#39;s IT requirements are captured and integrated into the overall building program and that the interfaces between work streams are communicated and managed effectively.\r\n</br> </br> Our value is most evident in complex corporate real estate projects that involve a high proportion of technology infrastructure such as trading floors, data centres and machine rooms.\r\n</br> We have significant experience in the design, procurement, implementation and migration management of large scale, high-profile office relocations and restacks and our consultants have managed projects that involve thousands of users, multiple locations and diverse corporate cultures.\r\n</br> </br>Our services include:\r\n<ul class=\"list-style\"> \r\n<li> Site selection and due diligence </li>\r\n<li> Vendor independent IT strategy </li>\r\n<li> Definition and procurement </li>\r\n<li> Implementation and migration management </li>\r\n<li> MAC and Churn </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n \r\n</br> <strong> Data Centre Services </strong>\r\n</br> </br> ITCS Group work with medium and large organisations to deliver their data centre requirements. The high capital and operational costs involved with building and running Data Centres requires specialist knowledge to ensure effective return on investment and that operations consistently deliver against the service levels demanded by the business.\r\n</br> </br> Our consultants work in partnership with Mechanical and Electrical designers and engineers to ensure that appropriate power, space and cooling is provisioned and that the technology space is optimised for efficiency, reliability and scalability.\r\n</br></br> Our Services include:\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Data Centre strategy </li>\r\n<li> Audit and inventory management </li>\r\n<li> Site evaluation, due diligence and selection </li>\r\n<li> Specification of IT requirements into facilities and M&E design </li>\r\n<li> IT infrastructure design and fit-out management </li>\r\n<li> Network, storage and core systems implementation </li>\r\n<li> Server consolidation and virtualization </li>\r\n<li> Application migration </li>\r\n<li> Data Centre Operations Outsourcing </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</br> <strong> Technology Investment </strong>\r\n</br> </br> The ITCS Group is vendor independent. Our independence gives our clients the assurance that the advice they receive from us is in their best interests and we build long term relationships based on our trusted advisor status.\r\n</br> </br> As an independent third party we are frequently engaged to provide governance, accountability and impartiality to the selection and procurement of technology.\r\n</br> </br> Our services include:\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Business and IT requirements definition </li>\r\n<li> Vendor independent technology strategy and definition </li>\r\n<li> Market evaluation and benchmarking </li>\r\n<li> Independent RFI and RFP management\r\n<li> Supplier evaluation and contract negotiation </li>\r\n</ul>', 'ITConsultingandProjectManagement.php', 'ITCS Group specialise in assisting organisations to deliver change within their IT environment. Our experienced consultants are expertly qualified in handling ... '),
(2, 2, '<style>\nh6 {\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\n}\n</style>Managed Services and Dynamic Staffing', 'images/service2.jpeg', 'ITCS Group provides highly skilled and experienced resources for Project Management, Application Development & Infrastructure services.\r\n\r\n</br> </br> Depending upon our client&#39;s procurement needs ITCS Group can provide the following:\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Fix Priced Managed or Outsourced Services </li> \r\n<li> Project based teams </li> \r\n<li> Individual Temporary Consultants </li> \r\n<li> Permanent Placements </li> \r\n<li> Interim Management </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n \r\n</br> ITCS Group specialize in providing staffing solutions in the following resource categories:\r\n\r\n</br> </br> <strong> IT Program and Project Management </strong> \r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Program and Project Managers </li>\r\n<li> PMO management and administration </li>\r\n<li> Service Delivery Management </li>\r\n<li> Business Analysts </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> IT Infrastructure Services  </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Wintel support, engineering and systems administration </li>\r\n<li> UNIX support, engineering and systems administration </li> \r\n<li> Database analysts and administration </li>\r\n<li> Virtualisation engineering </li> \r\n<li> Storage engineering and support </li>\r\n<li> Data Centre management </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> Trading Infrastructure & Market Data  </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Market Data analysts </li>\r\n<li> Market Data support and management </li> \r\n<li> Trading Infrastructure </li>\r\n<li> Messaging and Middleware </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> Information Security </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Information Risk </li>\r\n<li> Information Security Officers </li>\r\n<li> Information Security analysts </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> End User Computing and Desktop support </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Desktop support </li>\r\n<li> Application packaging and deployment </li>\r\n<li> MAC and Churn staff </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> Voice and Network  </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Network design, support and engineering </li>\r\n<li> Voice design, engineering and support </li> \r\n<li> Dealing systems and turrets </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong> Program & Application Development and Support </strong>\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'> \r\n<li> Java Developer </li>\r\n<li> Web Developer (HTML, PHP, JQuery, .NET, J2EE) </li>\r\n<li> VBA </li>\r\n<li> Analyst Programmer </li>\r\n<li> Business Analyst </li>\r\n<li> Fedessa Developer & Support </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</br> ITCS Group can offer tailored solutions where permanent in-house employees may not be the best choice or where sign-off for additional in-house headcount is not available. ITCS Group is also able to draw on an existing pool of experienced resources across the region that enables us to fill urgent vacancies quickly, helps us to resolve temporary resource shortages and provides expertise including on an ad-hoc or part-time basis.', 'ManagedServicesandDynamicStaffing.php', 'ITCS Group provide highly skilled and experienced resources, including Desktop and Helpdesk support, Move Add Change (MAC), Unix and Wintel Server, Network, Voice, ...'),
(3, 3, '<style>\nh6 {\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\n}\n</style>App Development and Off-shoring Advisory', 'images/service3.jpeg', 'ITCS Group provides Application Development Services, Programming Resources and Outsourcing to Global Companies across the Asia Pacific Region.\r\n\r\n</br> </br> From niche, one-off application development projects to ongoing development, integration and enhancement services we work across multiple sectors.\r\n\r\n</br> </br> Our services include:\r\n<ul class=\'list-style\'>\r\n<li> Front and back office platform development </li>\r\n<li> In-house software consulting and resourcing </li>\r\n<li> Application Development outsourcing </li>\r\n<li> Application Support and Management services </li>\r\n<li> Off-shoring advisory and transition services </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'ApplicationDevelopmentandOff-shoringAdvisory.php', 'ITCS Group provides Application Development Services, Programming Resources and Outsourcing to Global Companies across the Asia Pacific Region ...'),
(4, 4, '<style>\nh6 {\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\n}\n</style>IT Support', 'images/service1.jpg', 'ITCS is committed to provide high quality and SLA based managed services. Our services are designed to support you in short or long term initiatives to reduce costs and improve performance levels. Our IT professionals act as an extension to your technical teams by providing remote support, helpdesk support, office set up and IMAC services or as required to meet your changing needs.\r\n\r\n<br> <br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'row\'>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Regional Remote Support                   	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> System Monitoring, Track Server, Desktop, Network Downtime </li>\r\n			<li> Remote Log-in and Fix Router </li>\r\n			<li> Ticket Issuing Mechanism </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'row\'>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Local Desktop Service                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> On-site User Support </li>\r\n			<li> PC, Smart Phone, Structured Cabling, Recording System, Printer </li>\r\n			<li> 100% Delivery Uptime </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'row\'>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		IMAC Local Specific Service                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> Hardware and Software Installation </li>\r\n			<li> Office and Equipment Move </li>\r\n			<li> Add New Component in Office Environment </li>\r\n			<li> Change Office Elements to Comply with Business Needs </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'row\'>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Regional Office Setup                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> End-to-end Approach </li>\r\n			<li> Vendor Management </li>\r\n			<li> Project and IT Environment Management </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n', 'ITSupport.php', 'ITCS is committed to provide high quality and SLA based managed services. Our services are designed to support you in short or long term initiatives to reduce costs and improve performance levels. Our IT professionals act as an extension to your technical teams by providing remote support, helpdesk support, office set up and IMAC services or as required to meet your changing needs.\r\n\r\n<br> <br>\r\n\r\n<strong>Regional Remote Support</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>System Monitoring, Track Server, Desktop, Network Downtime</li>\r\n    <li>Remote Log-in and Fix Router</li>\r\n    <li>Ticket Issuing Mechanism</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Local Desktop Service</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>On-site User Support</li>\r\n    <li>PC, Smart Phone, Structured Cabling, Recording System, Printer</li>\r\n    <li>100% Delivery