(5, 5, '<style>\r\nh6 {\r\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\r\n}\r\n</style>Windows 10 Migration', 'images/service2.jpeg', 'ITCS Group has extensive experiences with Windows 10 migration on a global scale for renowned financial institutions and SMEs in the regions. We can provide the expertise to help you execute this migration while lowering costs, improving efficiencies, reducing risk and bring about a competitive advantage.\r\n\r\n<br> <br>\r\n\r\n<div class=‘row’>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Governance and Framework                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> Strong project and program management </li>\r\n			<li> Real-time accurate inventories </li>\r\n			<li> Application testing/packaging and certification </li>\r\n			<li> Centralized Command and Control Centre </li>\r\n			<li> Gradual ramp-up of migrations </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             	\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=‘row’>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Inventory Management            	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> Software profiles </li>\r\n			<li> Applications and their Windows 10 readiness status </li>\r\n			<li> Hardware profiles per user </li>\r\n			<li> Progress and issues </li>\r\n			<li> Reporting / Metrics functions (scheduled migrations, dropouts, progress) </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=‘row’>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Application Testing                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> Testing applications on Windows 10 </li>\r\n			<li> Support application owners with experience and manpower </li>\r\n			<li> Start with common applications </li>\r\n			<li> Gradually move towards more complex applications </li>\r\n			<li> Once certified, applications can be packaged and made available on Windows 10 </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=‘row’>\r\n<div class=\'panel panel-default box-shadow--4dp\'>\r\n					\r\n        <div class=\'panel-heading\' style=\'font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px !important; text-align: left;\'>\r\n    		Hardware Consolidations and Refresh                  	\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\'panel-body\'>\r\n        	<ul class=\'list-style\' style=\'margin-left: -25px !important; text-align: left !important;\'> \r\n			<li> Windows 10 may bring better hardware utilization and performance from new hardware </li>\r\n			<li> In compliance with company\'s hardware depreciation policy, assets can be replaced/adjusted during rollout </li>\r\n			<li> Opportunity to consolidate existing hardware footprint whilst reducing on-going maintenance support costs </li>\r\n   		</ul>\r\n             		\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Windows7Migration.php', 'ITCS Group has extensive experiences with Windows 7 migration on a global scale for renowned financial institutions and SMEs in the regions. The discontinuation of Microsoft&#39;s support of Windows XP from April 2014 onwards will incur substantial costs if you would like to extend the support of Windows XP or migrate to Windows 7. We can provide the expertise to help you execute this migration while lowering costs, improving efficiencies, reducing risk and bring about a competitive advantage.\r\n\r\n<br> <br>\r\n\r\n<strong>Governance and Framework</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Strong project and program management</li>\r\n    <li>Real-time accurate inventories</li>\r\n    <li>Application testing/packaging and certification</li>\r\n    <li>Centralised Command and Control Centre</li>\r\n    <li>Gradual ramp-up of migrations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Inventory Management</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Software profiles</li>\r\n    <li>Applications and their Windows 7 readiness status</li>\r\n    <li>Hardware profiles per user</li>\r\n    <li>Progress and issues</li>\r\n    <li>Reporting / Metrics functions (scheduled migrations, dropouts, progress)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Application Testing</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Testing applications on Windows 7</li>\r\n    <li>Support application owners with experience and manpower</li>\r\n    <li>Start with common applications</li>\r\n    <li>Gradually move towards more complex applications</li>\r\n    <li>Once certified, applications can be packaged and made available on Windows 7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Hardware Consolidations and Refresh</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Windows 7 may bring better hardware utilization and performance from new hardware</li>\r\n    <li>In compliance with company&rsquo;s hardware depreciation policy, assets can be replaced/adjusted during rollout</li>\r\n    <li>Opportunity to consolidate existing hardware footprint whilst reducing on-going maintenance support costs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(6, 6, '<style>\nh6 {\n    letter-spacing: 0px;\n}\n</style>IT Regulatory Advisory Services', 'images/service3.jpeg', 'Cybersecurity within licensed corporations (LC\'s) has, for some time, been of concern to the SFC/MAS, Japan FSA and is increasingly being viewed by the SFC/MAS, Japan FSA as a matter of priority given the ongoing occurrence of cybersecurity incidents being reported across the financial services industry. \r\n<br><br> \r\nMany LC\'s are struggling with SFC/MAS, Japan FSA regulatory understanding and more often than not, overspends on high-level advisory services without concrete deliverables (Policies & Procedures) that SFC and Japan FSA considers compliant. \r\n<br><br> \r\nA circular from SFC dated March 2016 and Japan FSA revised supplements January 2016 requires LC\'s to take appropriate measures to critically review access and their IT framework, including seeking advice from external subject matter experts. \r\n<br><br> \r\nITCS understands the importance and has been providing first-class IT regulatory advice to LC\'s and banks. ITCS Subject Matter Experts will provide a <a href=\"#free\" data-toggle=\'modal\' data-backdrop=\'static\' data-keyboard=\'false\'><strong>Free Assessment</strong></a> to access if your firm is SFC/MAS, Japan FSA compliant or if improvements are necessary. \r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'modal fade\' id=\"free\">\r\n											<div class=\'modal-dialog\'>\r\n												<div class=\'modal-content\'>\r\n													<div class=\'modal-header\' style=\' background: #00768c !important; \'>\r\n														<button class=\'close\' data-dismiss=\'modal\'>&times;</button>\r\n														<h4 class=\'modal-title\' style=\' color: white !important; text-align: left !important;\'> <i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o fa-lg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color: white !important;\"></i> Free Assessment</h4>\r\n													</div><!-- end of modal-header-->\r\n													<div class=\'modal-body\'>\r\n														<h5 align=\'left\'